Actors: Jason Momoa, Sylvia Hoeks, Hera Hilmar
Plot: Far in a dystopian future, the human race has lost the sense of sight, and society has had to find new ways to interact, build, hunt, and to survive. All of that is challenged when a set of twins are born with sight.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Primetime Emmy. 8 wins & 13 nominations total
